---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="PlantsImpact | About">
  <section
    class="space-y-4 rounded-lg bg-white p-5 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200"
  >
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">UCDRE Gruppe 3</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      Positive externalities are benefits created for others without direct
      payment. Trees, plants, and flowers can improve urban comfort,
      biodiversity, and public well-being beyond private gardens.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      <strong>SDG 11 (Sustainable Cities and Communities):</strong> urban greening
      supports healthier, more resilient, and more livable neighborhoods.
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-700">
      <strong>SDG 13 (Climate Action):</strong> vegetation can contribute to carbon
      storage, heat mitigation, and local environmental adaptation.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
      Disclaimer: all coefficients in this demo are simplified estimates for
      proof-of-concept purposes and not scientific measurements.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
